## HPAI H5N1 in Denmark since last meeting

## All measures according to regulation (EU) 2020/687

- Primary outbreaks -HPAI H5N1
- Clinical suspicions
- Culled completed
- Disposed of by rendering
- Preliminary C&amp;D approved
- 3 and 10 km zones established
- Derogation for captive birds
- Screening in zones

